\id 2PE - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020 
\h 2 Petro 
\toc1 Petro Mar Ariyo 
\toc2 2 Petro 
\toc3 2Pet 
\mt1 2 Petro 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 An Simon Petro, misumba kendo jaote mar Yesu Kristo, 
\b  
\p Andikonu un joma oseyudo yie ma nengone tek marom gi yiewa nimar Nyasachwa kod Jawarwa Yesu Kristo ema nomiyowago kuom adierane: 
\b  
\p  
\v 2 Ngʼwono kod kwe mogundho obed kodu kumedo ngʼeyo Nyasaye kod Yesu ma Ruodhwa. 
\b  
\s1 Luong mar ja-Kristo 
\p  
\v 3 Teko mar Nyasaye maduongʼ osemiyowa gik moko duto ma wadwaro mondo wabed mangima ka waluoro Nyasaye, kuom ngʼeyo Jal mane oluongowa kuom duongʼne owuon kod berne.  
\v 4 Kuom magi osemiyowa singruokne maduongʼ kendo ma nengogi tek, mondo e kuom gigo unyalo kawo kit Nyasaye kendo mondo utony ua e kethruok ma gombo maricho ma pinyni kelo. 
\p  
\v 5 Kuom mano, temuru matek kaka unyalo mondo umed ber e yieu, to bende medeuru ngʼeyo;  
\v 6 to ngʼeyo to medeuru ritruok, to ritruok medeuru horuok, to horuok to medeuru luoro Nyasaye,  
\v 7 to luoro Nyasaye to medeuru ngʼwono mar owete; to ngʼwono mar owete to medeuru hera.  
\v 8 Nikech ka un gi kit timbego mogundho, to gibiro gengʼou mondo kik ubed joma nono ma ok nyag olemo e ngʼeyo ma un-go kuom Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo.  
\v 9 To ka ngʼato onge gi kidogi e ngimane to en ngʼama neno machiegni kendo ma muofu nimar wiye osewil ni ne osepwodhe oweyo richoge machon. 
\p  
\v 10 Emomiyo, jowetena, meduru bedo gi siso mar rito luong mane oluongugo kod yiero maru ka un gi adier. Nikech ka utimo gigi to ok unupodhi,  
\v 11 kendo unuyud rwak malich ei pinyruoth mochwere mar Ruodhwa kendo Jawarwa Yesu Kristo. 
\s1 Koro mar Muma 
\p  
\v 12 Omiyo pod aparonu wechegi, kata obedo ni ungʼeyogi kendo uguroru motegno e adiera makoro un-go.  
\v 13 Aparo ni en gima ber mondo achiew pachu ka pod anie kiru mar ringruokni,  
\v 14 nikech angʼeyo ni achiegni weyo kiruni mana kaka Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo osenyisa maler.  
\v 15 Kendo abiro temo matek mondo ane ni ka aseweyou to ubiro siko kuparo wechegi. 
\p  
\v 16 Ne ok waluwo sigendini ma dhano ochuogo gi riekone kane wanyisou teko kod biro mar Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo, to wawegi ne wan joneno mar duongʼne.  
\v 17 Nikech ne oyudo luor kod duongʼ kuom Nyasaye Wuoro kane dwol obirone moa e Duongʼ Mamalo Moloyo, kawacho niya, “Ma e Wuoda mahero, en ema chunya mor kode!”\f + \fr 1:17 \ft \xt Mat 17:5; Mar 9:7; Luk 9:35\f* 
\v 18 Wan wawegi ne wawinjo dwolno mane oa e poloni, kane wan kode ewi got maler. 
\p  
\v 19 Omiyo wawacho weche jonabi mane gikoro makoro oselernwa tiendgi. Ka uchiko itu ne wechegi to ubiro konyoru, nikech gichalo gi ler marieny kawuok e mudho, nyaka chop odiechiengʼno yawre mi ler mar sulwe mokinyi meny chunjeu.  
\v 20 To moloyo mago duto, nyaka ungʼe ni onge wach mokor mar Muma ma janabi nyalo loko tiendgi gi pache owuon.  
\v 21 Nikech weche mokor manie Muma ne ok owuok e pach dhano, to Nyasaye ema nomiyo ji owuoyo, ka gin e bwo teko mar Roho Maler. 
\c 2  
\s1 Kethruok mar jopuonj mag miriambo 
\p  
\v 1 To jonabi mag miriambo bende ne nitie e kind oganda Nyasaye e ndalo machon, mana kaka jopuonj mag miriambo bende biro bedo e dieru. Gibiro kelonu puonj mag miriambo lingʼ-lingʼ mondo giketh ji, ka gikwedo nyaka Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto mane owarogi kendo mano nomi gitiekre kendgi piyo piyo nono!  
\v 2 Ji mathoth noluw kit ngimagi mag anjawo makelo wichkuot, kendo ginimi ji nocha yo mar adiera.  
\v 3 Nikech bedo gi gombo mar yudo gik malangʼ, jopuonj mag miriambogo noywau gi sigendini magiseloso mag miriambo malombo ji; mondo gimau mwandu. To kum margi mane oiknegi chakre chon ritogi, kendo kethruokgi ok nodeki ma ok ochoponegi. 
\p  
\v 4 To ka Nyasaye ne ok oweyo ma ok okumo kata mana malaike mane oketho, to ne owitogi e gehena ma en mach ma ok tho, koketogi e mudho mandiwa ka girito kumgi;  
\v 5 to kane ok oweyo ma ok okumo koda ka piny machon, e kinde mane omiyo pi oyweyo joma ochayo Nyasaye, to Nowa mane yalo mondo ji otim timbe makare kaachiel gi ji abiriyo mamoko, to ne oreso;  
\v 6 to ka Nyasaye nongʼado bura ni Sodom gi Gomora mine owangʼo joma odakie miergo molokore buru, kendo mi oketogi ranyisi mar gima biro timore ne joma ochayo Nyasaye;  
\v 7 kendo ka Nyasaye noreso Lut ngʼat makare, mane chunye chandore malit nikech ngima mochido mar joma ne ochayo chik  
\v 8 (nikech ne en ngʼat makare, chunye ne chande malit kane oneno timbe maricho ma tiengʼ mane odakgo timo pile ka pile);  
\v 9 to ka en kamano, to kare Ruoth ongʼeyo kaka dores joma omiye luor kuom tembe ma giyudo kendo ongʼeyo kaka okano joma richo ni kum chiengʼ Bura, ka gidhi nyime kod kumgi.  
\v 10 Mani en adiera kuom jogo machopo dwaro mochido mag ringregi ka gichayo loch. 
\p Jopuonj mag miriambogi wengegi tek kendo opongʼ gi achaya, bende ok giluoro kata mana wuoyo marach kuom joma nigi joloch mag polo,  
\v 11 ma kata mana malaike man-gi teko gi duongʼ moloyogi ok nyal wuoyo marach kuom chwechgo e nyim Ruoth Nyasaye.  
\v 12 To jogi wuoyo marach ka giyanyo nyaka gik ma ok giwinj tiendgi. Gichalo le maonge rieko, mager, maonge paro, mane ochwe mana mondo omaki oyangʼ. Jogi biro lal nono mana ka le mag bungu. 
\p  
\v 13 Giniyud pok mar richo, kar richo magisetimo. Giwinjo maber ka gichopo gombo duto mag ringregi ratiro e nyim ji. Ka gidwanyore kendo gichopo gombogi maricho e chokruogeu mag sawo to gichalo mbelni kod gik motop.  
\v 14 Wengegi rango mon mana gigombo mar terruok kendo richo mitnegi ma ok giwe. Giywayo mon ma yiegi yomyom mondo gitimgo richo kendo gipongʼ gi wuoro. Jogi gin joma okwongʼ adier!  
\v 15 Gisebaro giweyo yo makare mi girwenyo ka giluwo yor Balaam wuod Beor, mane ohero misach richo.  
\v 16 To kanyna ne okwere kuom timne marachno, kata obedo ni en le ma ok wuo kamano, to ne owuoyo gi dwond dhano mi ogengʼo neko janabino. 
\p  
\v 17 Jogi gin sokni maonge pi kendo gichalo gi ongʼwengʼo ma yamo tero. Gima okan nigi mudho mandiwa molil ti.  
\v 18 Nikech giwacho weche manono mag sunga mopongʼ gi gombo maricho mag kit dhano mohero richo, mondo gimi joma tinde eka tony aa kuom joma olal tim richo.  
\v 19 Gisingore ni jogo ni gibiro miyogi thuolo to gin giwegi gin wasumbini mag richo makelo kethruok nikech dhano en misumba gimoro amora moloyo ngimane.  
\v 20 Ka ji osetony oweyo kethruok mar piny, nikech ngʼeyo Ruodhwa kendo Jawarwa Yesu Kristo, eka bangʼe gichako giduodore e kethruok mi kethruok omakogi kendo, to ngimagi machien bedo marach moloyo ngimagi mokwongo.  
\v 21 Dine obedo nigi maber moloyo ka dine ok gingʼeyo yor ngima makare, moloyo ngʼeyogo eka bangʼe gidok chien giweyo chik mane omigi.  
\v 22 Gima osetimorenigi chopo adiera mar ngero mawacho niya, “Guok dok e ngʼokne mosengʼogo”\f + \fr 2:22 \ft \xt Nge 26:11\f* kendo niya, “Anguro moseluoki odok ngʼielore e chwodho.” 
\c 3  
\s1 Biro mar Ruoth 
\p  
\v 1 Osiepena mageno, maa koro en barupa mar ariyo ma andikonu. Asendikonugi giduto kargi ariyo mondo aparnu kendo achiew pachu obed moyawore.  
\v 2 Adwaro ni mondo upar weche mane jonabi maler okoro chon kod chik mane omiu koa kuom Ruodhwa kendo Jawarwa kokadho kuom joote magu. 
\p  
\v 3 Mokwongo nyaka ungʼe ni e ndalo mogik jomoko machayo ji nobi ka gichayou kendo ka giluwo gombogi maricho.  
\v 4 Ka gipenjou niya “Ruodhu mane osingore ni onego bed ni duogono to ere? Donge nyaka ne kwerewa tho gik moko osebedo mana machalre nyaka aa chakruok chwech piny!”  
\v 5 To jogi wigi wil mar oyiem ni chon gi lala wach Nyasaye nomiyo polo obedo kendo piny ne ochwe koa kuom pi kendo pi ema nochweyego.  
\v 6 Kendo pigno nolokore ataro ma Nyasaye nokethego piny machon.  
\v 7 Kuom wach nogo ema omiyo polo gi piny masani okan ni mach. Okan-gi nyaka chop odiechiengʼno ma joma ochayo Nyasaye nongʼadnigi bura mi notiekgi chuth. 
\p  
\v 8 To wiu kik wil gi gimoro achielni osiepena mageno: Ni kuom Ruoth odiechiengʼ achiel chalre gi higni alufu achiel, kendo higni alufu achiel chalre gi odiechiengʼ achiel.  
\v 9 Ruoth ok odeko kuom chopo singruokne, kaka jomoko paro. Un ema oweyonu thuolo mondo ulokru, nikech ohore mos ka odwaro ni kik ngʼato lal kata achiel, to odwaro mondo ji duto olokre owe richogi. 
\p  
\v 10 To odiechieng Ruoth nobi apoya mana kaka jakuo. Polo noleny nono ka mor matek kendo gik mochwe manie kor polo nowangʼ mi keth chuth, to piny gi gik moko duto manie iye nolal nono. 
\p  
\v 11 Ka gigi duto ibiro kethi kamano, koro to onego ubed jomachal nadi? Onego udag e ngima maler kendo moluoro Nyasaye,  
\v 12 ka urito odiechiengʼ mar Nyasaye, kendo ka utemo beru mondo ochop piyo. Odiechiengʼno polo nowangʼ mi nokethe, kendo chwech mag polo noleny kawangʼ.  
\v 13 Wan to warito gik ma Nyasaye osesingonwa, ma en polo manyien gi piny manyien, kama timbe makare ema noyudre. 
\p  
\v 14 Emomiyo, osiepena mageno, ka pod urito odiechiengʼno to temuru matek kaka unyalo mondo ubed jomaler maonge ketho e nyim Nyasaye, kendo beduru gi kwe kode.  
\v 15 Beduru kungʼeyo ni deko mar Ruodhwa oweyo mana thuolo mar yudo warruok, mana kaka Paulo owadwa mwageno bende osendikonu gi rieko mane Nyasaye omiye.  
\v 16 Barupenego duto ondiko machalre, kowuoyo kuom wechegi. Barupene otingʼo weche moko ma tiendgi tek ma joma kia kaachiel gi jo-hubagabaga gwenyo, mana kaka gigwenyo Ndiko mamoko bende, to timgino biro kelonegi chandruok. 
\p  
\v 17 Emomiyo, osiepena mageno, kaka koro usengʼeyo wachni, ritreuru mondo kik ywau gi kethruok mag jomaricho mi ulwar ua kama ber muchungʼie.  
\v 18 To dhiuru nyime kudongo e ngʼwono kod ngʼeyo ma un-go kuom Ruodhwa kendo Jawarwa Yesu Kristo. 
\b  
\b  
\p En ema oyud duongʼ tinende kendo nyaka chiengʼ! Amin.